<!--
  Root source file for "Một số thuật ngữ trong Toán rời rạc".
  The book is organized as an A–Z lexicon: one chapter per English letter,
  one entry per English term. To edit content, edit the ch-*.ptx files.
  xml:lang stays en-US so that structural labels build reliably; the prose
  is Vietnamese. (Switching labels to Vietnamese is a later refinement.)
-->
